name: somewhere in bandung .02
description:
awkward adventure skate series 13/50.
o, bzjm & anak punk goes to bandung. the mecca of indonesian skateboarding. i draw this famous spot, taman lalu lintas skatepark based on my memory. i skated this park three times -yes three times i counted- around late 1990's with my buddies. having fun with locals. saw the 'big air' for the first time with my own bare eyes by local. still remember 'till today. 

drawing pen on paper. digital coloring.

2517 x 1772 5.47 MB
